{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;(...) and scary stories have been accompanying men for centuries. They have many faces and forms. But what is their purpose? <strong>Why do we enjoy being afraid so much?</strong> During our therapy, I'll try to (...)&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(excerpt from <strong>Dr. Emmerson's Clinic</strong> leaflet)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/screen_desc_01.png?t=1730124482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Try out our original approach to bringing literature into the interactive medium</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1730124482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter the world of weird fiction and cosmic horror masterpieces. Experience them in<strong> complete, uncut versions</strong>, created with full respect to their authors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/screen_desc_02.png?t=1730124482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Dr. Emmerson's Nocturnes</i> is a collection of <strong>fully-voiced visual novel games in real-time 3D</strong>. If you are interested in the concept, we encourage you to check out our highly acclaimed <strong>completely FREE</strong> adaptation of <strong>Dagon - H. P. Lovecraft's</strong> first story connected to the famous Cthulhu Mythos: </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/STEAM_460_215_png.png?t=1730124482\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">-- <strong>15% of revenue will be donated to charity organizations</strong> --</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(chosen by our community on Discord) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1730124482\" />Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> fully-voiced <strong>narrative experience</strong> in real-time 3D </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>VR </strong>support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>3-4 stories</strong> (maybe more - Dr. Emmerson often adjusts his treatment) written by the best weird fiction authors including <strong>H. P. Lovecraft</strong> and <strong>Stefan Grabi\u0144ski</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> dozens of <strong>interesting facts</strong> about the authors and their masterpieces hidden inside the game </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1730124482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/screen_desc_04.png?t=1730124482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So relax and let Dr. Emmerson guide you through all the <strong>colors of dread</strong>. Don't be afraid, these are just stories, they can't hurt you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>?yeht naC</i></strong></h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730124482","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730124482","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/capsule_231x87_alt_assets_1.jpg?t=1730124482","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/capsule_184x69_alt_assets_1.jpg?t=1730124482","categories":[{"description":"Si